OL,7,FA fire which ripped through a well-
OL,8,Fknown Hampshire pub was caused by a
OL,9,Ffaulty tumble dryer, fire crews have
OL,10,Frevealed.
OL,12,FAround fifty firefighters were
OL,13,Ftackling the blaze at it's height,
OL,14,Fwhich broke out at Osborne View in
OL,15,FHill Head in the early hours of
OL,16,FThursday. (22 February)
OL,18,FThe pub was completely gutted by the
OL,19,Fblaze and crews remain at the scene as
OL,20,Fan investigation is launched.
