OL,7,F"I think the pub's such a sort of
OL,8,Fcornerstone of Hill Head, there isn't
OL,9,Fthat much business there, and there's
OL,10,Fnot that many pubs, so it's just
OL,11,Freally a tragedy that it's happened.
OL,13,F"I'm glad that everyone's safe and
OL,14,Feveryone's unharmed and, you know,
OL,15,Fgreat work by the fire engines to put
OL,16,Feverything out, but yeah, it's
OL,17,Fworrying to know what will happen next
OL,18,Freally."
