OL,7,FIn a statement, Matt Kearsey, Managing
OL,8,FDirector of Hall & Woodhouse, said: "A
OL,9,Fserious fire broke out at the Osborne
OL,10,FView Hotel in Fareham in the early
OL,11,Fhours of this morning (Thursday 22nd
OL,12,FFebruary).
OL,14,F"Thankfully, all team onsite evacuated
OL,15,Fbefore coming to any harm. The
OL,16,Fwellbeing of all those affected is our
OL,17,Fprimary concern and we will be
OL,18,Fproviding support and reassurance to
OL,19,Fall those who require it.
